snippet.title: CONFIRMED Johnny Depp Officially Rehired By Disney As Jack Sparrow
snippet.description:
CONFIRMED Johnny Depp Officially Rehired By Disney As Jack Sparrow
For months, if not years, a certain movement has been going on outside of a certain courtroom battle. Mainly in that of the fight between Johnny Depp and his ex-wife in Amber Heard. She's accused him of being an during their one-year marriage, and Depp fought back with evidence that she was the all along. This led to a major court case spanning two continents that is STILL being battled over right now. And just as important, it's left Johnny Depp without some key roles in films. But now, that MIGHT be over via...a video game. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

So what do you think? What do you think of this look at Sea of Thieves and how they incorporated Pirates of the Caribbean into it? Are you sad that this isn't Johnny Depp portraying Jack Sparrow?
